These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
House: victorian, farmhouse, wooden, craftsman
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, blood-red, chestnut
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, puzzles, rock-climbing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, musical, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, jazz, rock
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, balloon-flower, amaryllis, marigold
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, alhambra, oliveros, siglo
 1. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching adventure movies is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 3. the person who likes chestnut is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 5. the oliveros-smoker is between the bolivar-smoker and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the victorian house is the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching musical movies is the farmhouse house##1
10. the wooden house is in an even position##4
11. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
12. the victorian house is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
13. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the fan of rock##1
14. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
16. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4
17. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3
18. the person who growsmarigold is the siglo-smoker##1
19. the fan of folk is the person who likes light-blue##1
20. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
21. the person watching adventure movies is the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| House      | craftsman        | wooden   | victorian         | farmhouse  |
| Color          | blood-red         | fuchsia   | light-blue   | chestnut |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | puzzles    | video-games | drawing   |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | adventure  | satire      | musical   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz          | rock       | folk        | ambient   |
| Flower           | marigold        | amaryllis      | aconite    | balloon-flower    |
| Cigar         | siglo | oliveros | bolivar      | alhambra   |

