House: cottage, townhouse, futuristic, farmhouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey, skateboarding, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, train, trike
 1. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 2. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 5. the person playing scrabble is the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
10. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the bus is the person traveling to boston##1
12. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
13. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person playing domino##1
17. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
18. the townhouse house is the person driving the trike##1
19. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
20. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
21. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |    4     |
